#

Savory Herb Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishComfort FoodEasy Recipe

Description

Creamy mashed potatoes infused with aromatic herbs for a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 2 pounds
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • dried thyme: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
